room_title: Escape room "Grandpa's Lottery" by Aiken 2 Escape in Aiken
room_description: Grandpa Charlie has been playing the same lottery numbers every week since you were "knee-high to a grasshopper"! He has finally won the jackpot, but poor Grandpa can't remember where he put the ticket! You and your crazy cousins have one hour to find the ticket before the lottery closes!
